HILLTOP &#8211; The R40 between Mbombela and Barbertonis was closed for trucks after a freight truck loaded with building material veered off the road last night.Also read: Truck transporting chain store clothing catches fire on R40The wreck is not visible from the road. Aerial footage shows that, after veering off the road, the truck rambled downhill along a slope and came to a standstill after about 150 metres. Technicians were working at retrieving the wreck.The driver of the truck has was not injured.Also read: Truck drives right through White River pubLowvelder will provide more information as it becomes available.Video footage: James Munro